  "text": "The subjects' consonant errors were pooled and converted to confusion matrices for the A, V, and AV conditions as shown in Table 1, Table 2, and Table 3 , respectively. The matrix for each condition was submitted to a Sequential Information Analysis (SINFA) [CITATION_1] , to determine if different types and amounts of information were transmitted by selected a priori features . The features specified for this analysis are provided in Table 4 .",
